elements.name: Change the status of a Post

steps.name: I enter "<EMAIL>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector "ol.posts-list.gh-list li a.gh-post-list-status > div > span.gh-content-status-published"
I click on element having css selector "div.gh-publishmenu > div.gh-publishmenu-trigger"
I click on element having css selector "div.gh-publishmenu-radio-label"
I click on element having css selector "button.gh-publishmenu-button"
